      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RAZOR HAYZE (8) took the sit on the lead but levelled up to score (29.70) at this track in a Grade 6 over 520m. Won at her only start from this draw. In form and can go on with it. CANYA TALK NOW (5) won again in an impressive display after running them ragged to make it two on the bounce, scoring by 6 lengths (24.99) at Q Lakeside over 457m. The form out of last race has been strong. Sure to measure up. KONSTANTIN (2) is rarely far away but tends to find one better, placing 19 from 31 starts. Continues to race well, filling the minors at the last three starts, the latest when third (29.81) at this track. Has never missed the frame here from three starts. Comes through a solid form race last start. Can feature again. SPECIFICALLY (1) hit the frame here last time and looks a chance again.",
